item.title: I wonder how much bit bay is going to worth in the future
item.dc:creator: @GiorgosK Giorgos Kontopoulos
item.description:
@GiorgosK wrote:

Nobody can predict such a thing

Everyone involved in BitBay believes it has utility and the team based with roadmap in mind is taking the right actions in order to improve upon what is there and get a better adoption (users using it).

We welcome feedback on things to be done or ideas but there is also many open positions for people that want to actively participate and make sure this project sees the amount of attention it deserves.

Thank you for stoping by, great to see you here.
